comments: Sharpe (POR) is established in Paul's (GSW) path prior to absorbing the marginal body contact that occurs as they come together inside half-court.
Looney (GSW) turns slightly as he firms up over his left foot and he does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the screen on Grant (POR).
Grant (POR) briefly has his arms around Looney's (GSW) upper half before correcting as he goes over the pick.
Ayton (POR) and Curry (GSW) engage and disengage with one another after coming together at the same spot off-ball.
Sharpe (POR) and Wiggins (GSW) jump toward one another as they pursue the rebound and incidental arm/body contact occurs when they come together in the air.
Simons (POR) and Curry (GSW) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Ayton (POR) avoids making contact with Curry (GSW) prior to Curry losing control of the ball after dribbling into Looney's (GSW) back.
Wiggins (GSW) jumps from point A to point B and initiates body contact that alters Simons' (POR) driving shot attempt.
Ayton (POR) briefly has his hands on Looney's (GSW) sides before quickly releasing.
Curry (GSW) brushes Brogdon's (POR) left side from behind and marginal contact occurs after Brogdon's gather.
Looney (GSW) jumps from point A to point B and initiates body contact that causes Sharpe (POR) to become dislodged after the release of his put-back attempt.
Sharpe (POR) extends forward into Paul's (GSW) path and initiates body contact that affects Paul's SQBR at the top of the perimeter.
Sharpe (POR) brushes Paul's (GSW) right side and marginal contact occurs as Paul dribbles alongside the lane line.
Kuminga (GSW) moves forward into Simons (POR) and initiates body contact as Simons cuts back toward the basket after his gather, altering the driving shot attempt.
Grant (POR) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Curry (GSW) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Possession is awarded to Golden State. However, the ball touches Curry's (GSW) left leg last before going out of bounds. Possession should have been awarded to Portland.
Wiggins (GSW) grasps and then quickly releases his hand away from Grant's (POR) left shoulder during the inbound.
Grant (POR) commits a take foul on Wiggins (GSW).
Grant (POR) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Wiggins (GSW) brings his right hand forward as he pursues the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Ayton's (POR) left arm when Ayton secures the ball.
Curry (GSW) brings his hand toward Sharpe's (POR) right side and marginal contact occurs as Sharpe dribbles in transition.
Podziemski (GSW) beats Sharpe (POR) to the spot and establishes a legal guarding position in Sharpe's path prior to Sharpe initiating the contact during the driving shot attempt.
Sharpe (POR) commits a take foul on Podziemski (GSW).
